{
  "stem": "24106.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother cooked something, which she prepared on the table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just sit to eat about something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "An alert, I mean, the bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what we do, we leave-- left everything and we're running across to that place to hide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, my mo-- my mother was running, she lost her slipper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she didn't go-- she went without-- without a slipper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and the back of that building, it was like a lumber yard-- a lot of lumber.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father was running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My sister, my mother, and I was after them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we didn't go into that building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, let's go to the-- we'll hide under the [NON-ENGLISH], under the-- the lumber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It maybe took about 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when walked out from that place, the roof was on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody got killed in that place, that we were always going there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We heard a lot of screaming and a lot of wounded were running out with bloody people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father said, we're not staying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We're going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We're not-- we're going to-- everybody's going to get killed here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's with my father, my mother, my sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that like I start to tell you, we went to-- we were already in Krasnodarskiy Krai.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's what we survived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took us about three weeks from Rostov to go-- my father wants to go-- to Georgia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, over there, is a war-- a warm climate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No winter there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No-- only what we were wearing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when we stopped, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like I said, it was about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And going down this way, they-- they stopped us in [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Baku. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
